  <row Id="222" PostTypeId="1" AcceptedAnswerId="406" CreationDate="2010-08-26T07:04:10.370" Score="4" ViewCount="2437" Body="&lt;p&gt;I have struggled for a while with &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iliotibial_Band_Syndrome&quot;&gt;Illiotibial Band&lt;/a&gt; pain or &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iliotibial_Band_Syndrome&quot;&gt;Illiotibial Band Friction Syndrome&lt;/a&gt; when cycling and running, here are some of the things that I have done to get rid of the pain:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When it is inflammed:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.drugs.com/mtm/cataflam.html&quot;&gt;Cataflam&lt;/a&gt; (a non-steroidal anti-inflammatory - &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Non-steroidal_anti-inflammatory_drug&quot;&gt;NSAID&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Ice&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Transact patches (topical anti-inflammatory)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Rest&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Prevention:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Hamstring strectches&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Massage (cross friction on ITB)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Strengthening of &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gluteus_medius_muscle&quot;&gt;gluteus medius&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Stretching of gluteus medius and &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tensor_fasciae_latae&quot;&gt;TFL&lt;/a&gt; (Tensor Fascia Latae)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Foam &lt;a href=&quot;http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-679683274642732742#&quot;&gt;roller&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Bike setup correction (moving saddle forward worked for me)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;There are some good resources on the Internet, here are some I have read:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.irishcycling.com/publish/news/art_4249.shtml&quot;&gt;Cycling Problems - ITB Pain And Tightness&lt;/a&gt;, by Karen Doyle&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a 