in-or-a-chainseparate-bought-master-link&quot;&gt;spare master links&lt;/a&gt; (good insurance in the case of a chain break)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;cable-actuated disc brakes or rim-brakes, more &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.adventurecycling.org/features/givemeabrake.cfm&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;a lot of good stuff &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.adventurecycling.org/features/howto.cfm#Gear&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; for traveling&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;" OwnerDisplayName="user652" LastEditorDisplayName="user652" LastEditDate="2011-02-22T18:19:41.360" LastActivityDate="2011-02-22T18:19:41.360" Title="Items required in a World travelling bike?" Tags="&lt;touring&gt;&lt;touring-bikes&gt;" AnswerCount="4" CommentCount="5" FavoriteCount="1" />
