uter, but I'm certainly sold on mudguards/fenders for now.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;" OwnerUserId="1588" LastEditorUserId="76" LastEditDate="2011-08-21T20:46:38.807" LastActivityDate="2012-06-11T12:33:30.897" Title="Do mudguards/fenders help? If so, what are the best for a fixie commuter?" Tags="&lt;product-rec&gt;&lt;accessories&gt;&lt;commuting-bike&gt;&lt;fenders&gt;" AnswerCount="7" CommentCount="4" FavoriteCount="1" />
