king, so even the simplest advice would be appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;" OwnerUserId="4186" LastActivityDate="2012-08-14T19:39:34.717" Title="Avoiding being wiped out after work commute?" Tags="&lt;commuter&gt;&lt;health&gt;&lt;diet&gt;" AnswerCount="6" CommentCount="3" FavoriteCount="2" />
