 everything that would be forming the scab. I would leave the band-aids off more, but I'm still biking into work and wearing jeans there. &lt;strong&gt;How should I be taking care of the wound now?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Any advice is appreciated! &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;" OwnerUserId="4186" LastActivityDate="2012-08-17T06:18:25.710" Title="Dealing with a scrape (cleaning a wound)?" Tags="&lt;health&gt;&lt;injury&gt;&lt;damage&gt;" AnswerCount="2" CommentCount="8" FavoriteCount="1" ClosedDate="2012-08-17T09:04:42.400" />
